author: Fiona Flynn
title: Soap | Emmerdale - entertainment.ie
text: An awake Robert is rightly worried that Aaron wasn't the shooter and wants the police to guard his door. He suggests that Chrissie framed Aaron and she enjoys the look of fear in his eye as she toys with him. However, Robert isn't the only one with a price on his head as someone is plotting a thousand painful deaths for another resident. Jaysus...can't they all just get along?
